  <header class="article-header">
    <h1>Rock and Roll Hall of Fame Music Masters 2015: Date, Time and How to Watch Online</h1>
    <div class="by-line">
      <a title="Liz Rowley's Profile" class="link-author avatar avatar-small" href="../../profiles/188915/liz-rowley">
        <img alt="Liz Rowley's avatar image" class="no-share-btns" src="http://media3.mic.com/Yjg1OTc5MmE3MyMvUlJlOG5IXzJHWW56QWFxbmNmR3B1S2REbDJNPS8yNXgyNS9zbWFydC9odHRwczovL3MzLmFtYXpvbmF3cy5jb20vcG9saWN5bWljLWltYWdlcy9hYjM2NWM0OWFmZmU2NjFhZDRkMDVmZTFkN2FmZmY4OWQ0MzllNDlkYzE4OGVhMWJlNzljMjJiODBiOTk3MTg3LmpwZw==.jpg">
      </a>
      By
      <a title="Liz Rowley's Profile" class="link-author name" href="../../profiles/188915/liz-rowley">Liz Rowley</a>
      <time datetime="2015-11-06T18:39:32.000Z" pubdate="">November 06, 2015</time>
    </div>
    <div class="share-facebook-twitter subhead">
      <span class="fb-like-container-text">Like Mic on Facebook:</span>
      <span class="fb-button">
        <div class="fb-like-top fb-like" data-href="https://www.facebook.com/MicMedia" data-width="300" data-keen-tracking-name="subhed" data-keen-social-channel="facebook" data-show-faces="false" data-send="false" data-layout="button"></div>
      </span>
    </div>
  </header>
  <div id="article-body" class="article-body share-media-toolbar-block"><div class="share-media share-media-side-fold">
  <ul><li class="share-media-facebook"><div class="share-button-count"><a href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmic.com%2Farticles%2F128086%2Frock-and-roll-hall-of-fame-music-masters-2015-date-time-and-how-to-watch-online" title="Share on Facebook" rel:gt_act="share/facebook/share" rel:gt_label="true" name="fb_share" target="_new" class="share-button share-button-medium-facebook modal-trigger-facebook k-trackable-share" data-fb-link="http://mic.com/articles/128086/rock-and-roll-hall-of-fame-music-masters-2015-date-time-and-how-to-watch-online" data-keen-tracking-name="sidefold-share" data-keen-social-channel="facebook" data-popup-height="380" data-popup-width="660" data-facebook-pixel-id="6028307573536"><i class="social-icon-mini social-icon-mini-facebook"></i><i class="social-icon-divider"></i>SHARE</a></div></li>
<li class="share-media-twitter"><div class="share-button-count"><a href="http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fmic.com%2Farticles%2F128086%2Frock-and-roll-hall-of-fame-music-masters-2015-date-time-and-how-to-watch-online&amp;original_referer=http%3A%2F%2Fmic.com%2Farticles%2F128086%2Frock-and-roll-hall-of-fame-music-masters-2015-date-time-and-how-to-watch-online&amp;related=MicNews&amp;source=tweetbutton&amp;text=Rock%20and%20Roll%20Hall%20of%20Fame%20Music%20Masters%202015%3A%20Date%2C%20Time%20and%20How%20to%20Watch%20Online&amp;via=MicNews" title="Share on Twitter" target="_new" class="share-button share-button-medium-twitter k-trackable-share" data-keen-tracking-name="sidefold-share" data-keen-social-channel="twitter" data-popup-height="380" data-popup-width="660" data-facebook-pixel-id="6028307573536"><i class="social-icon-mini social-icon-mini-twitter"></i><i class="social-icon-divider"></i>TWEET</a></div></li>
<li class="share-media-tumblr"><div class="share-button-count"><a href="http://tumblr.com/share/link?url=http%3A%2F%2Fmic.com%2Farticles%2F128086%2Frock-and-roll-hall-of-fame-music-masters-2015-date-time-and-how-to-watch-online&amp;description=All%20hail%20Smokey%20Robinson!&amp;name=Rock%20and%20Roll%20Hall%20of%20Fame%20Music%20Masters%202015%3A%20Date%2C%20Time%20and%20How%20to%20Watch%20Online" title="Share on Tumblr" target="_new" class="share-button share-button-medium-tumblr k-trackable-share" data-keen-tracking-name="sidefold-share" data-keen-social-channel="tumblr" data-popup-width="450" data-popup-height="483" data-facebook-pixel-id="6028307573536"><i class="social-icon-mini social-icon-mini-tumblr"></i><i-social-icon-divider></i-social-icon-divider>POST</a></div></li></ul>
  <div class="corner"></div>
</div>
<div class="article-body-content"><p class="">The Rock and Roll Hall of Fame's 20th annual Music Masters series, a <a href="https://rockhall.com/event/Rock-Hall-Music-Masters-Smokey-Robinson-2015/">weeklong</a>&nbsp;set of events that celebrate the living legends of the music industry, will culminate on Saturday with a tribute concert and awards ceremony to honor soul king Smokey Robinson, who was inducted into the Hall of Fame in 1987. The event will take place at Playhouse Square's State Theatre in Cleveland&nbsp;at at 7:30 p.m Eastern.</p>
<p class="">Though the event won't be streaming online, a limited number of <a href="https://rockhall.com/event/Rock-Hall-Music-Masters-Smokey-Robinson-2015/">tickets</a>&nbsp;are still available to the tribute concert, and the event organizers may show footage from the event on the Rock and Roll Hall of Fame <a href="https://www.youtube.com/user/rockhall">YouTube channel</a>.&nbsp;</p>
<p class="">This year's concert boasts performances from three Hall of Fame inductees: Dennis Edwards of the Temptations (1989), Martha Reeves of Martha and the Vandellas (1995) and Mary Wilson of the Supremes (1988). Other performers on Saturday include Avant, AverySunshine, Bilal, JoJo, Eric Roberson, the Robert Glasper Experiment and Michelle Williams. Though Robinson will be in Cleveland to accept the honor, he is not expected to perform.</p>
<figure contenteditable="false" data-url="https://twitter.com/KlipschAudio/status/662404088626221056" class="embeddable clearfix embeddable-twitter embeddable-twit-pic" data-twitterhtml="<blockquote lang=&quot;en&quot; class=&quot;twitter-tweet&quot;><p>The Klipsch Audio Stage at the @Rock_Hall honors Smokey Robinson. pic.twitter.com/6jQFSWqvnn</p><a href=&quot;https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CTDR7ksUEAEUF-D.jpg:large&quot;>https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CTDR7ksUEAEUF-D.jpg:large</a><a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/KlipschAudio/status/662404088626221056&quot;></a><script async=&quot;async&quot; src=&quot;//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js&quot; charset=&quot;utf-8&quot;></script></blockquote>" id="embeddable-oo43m3o" data-type="twitter"><div class="embeddable-container"><blockquote lang="en" class="twitter-tweet"><p>The Klipsch Audio Stage at the @Rock_Hall honors Smokey Robinson. pic.twitter.com/6jQFSWqvnn</p><a href="https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CTDR7ksUEAEUF-D.jpg:large">https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CTDR7ksUEAEUF-D.jpg:large</a><a href="https://twitter.com/KlipschAudio/status/662404088626221056"></a><script async="async" src="http://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></blockquote></div></figure>
<figure contenteditable="false" class="embeddable clearfix embeddable-facebook" data-facebookhtml="<div id=&quot;fb-root&quot;></div><div data-href=&quot;https://www.facebook.com/rockandrollhalloffame/videos/10153361408004107/&quot; class=&quot;fb-post noclick&quot;><div class=&quot;fb-xfbml-parse-ignore&quot;></div></div>" id="embeddable-2s6tpng" data-type="facebook"><div class="embeddable-container"><div id="fb-root"></div><div data-href="https://www.facebook.com/rockandrollhalloffame/videos/10153361408004107/" class="fb-post noclick"><div class="fb-xfbml-parse-ignore"></div></div></div></figure>
<p class="">Between 1960 and 1971, Smokey Robinson and the Miracles&nbsp;churned out <a href="https://rockhall.com/pressroom/announcements/smokey-robinson-amm-2015/">27&nbsp;beloved hits</a>&nbsp;for Motown Records, among them "The Tracks of My Tears," "You've Really Got a Hold on Me," "Shop Around" and "I Second That Emotion." Later on, Robinson collaborated with the likes of Marvin Gaye, the Temptations, Mary Wells and the Marvelettes. Most recently, Robinson has focused his attentions on a solo career, releasing a gospel album called <i>Food for the Spirit</i> in 2014.&nbsp;</p>
<figure contenteditable="false" data-youtube-id="rNS6D4hSQdA" class="embeddable clearfix embeddable-video embeddable-youtube" id="embeddable-uao501" data-type="youtube">
  <div class="embeddable-container">
    <div class="lazyYT" data-youtube-id="rNS6D4hSQdA" data-ratio="16:9"></div>
  </div>
  <figcaption class="article-embeddable-attribution">Source: <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rNS6D4hSQdA" class="article-embeddable-source">YouTube</a></figcaption>
</figure>
<p class="">"Smokey Robinson's accomplishments as a songwriter, performer, and producer are unparalleled," said&nbsp;Lauren Onkey,&nbsp;the Rock and Roll Hall of Fame's vice president of education and public programs, in a&nbsp;<a href="https://rockhall.com/pressroom/announcements/smokey-robinson-amm-2015/#sthash.HEBM0xQA.dpuf">statement</a>. "It is particularly fitting that we honor him this year, the 20th year of Music Masters. The longstanding popularity and impact of his work shows us the power of popular music in our lives, which is what Music Masters is all about."</p>
<figure contenteditable="false" class="embeddable clearfix image article-image-container article-image-container-horizontal photo embeddable-image" id="embeddable-jv7823o" data-type="image"><div class="embeddable-container"><img src="http://thumbs.mic.com/NmU4YjRlZDZkMiMvay1jRENPNS1ITjFOUV9FN1JmbUFXRnF6R2pnPS8zMHg3OTM6MjI5N3gyMTI3LzkwMHg1MzAvZmlsdGVyczpxdWFsaXR5KDcwKS9odHRwOi8vczMuYW1hem9uYXdzLmNvbS9wb2xpY3ltaWMtaW1hZ2VzLzNzOWduOWhjeGw3c3Eyd2pxOW5mY3RoeWtsZnA5bDN5MzB2NGJqZGhpN3Zja2FsMWVxc3F4Zm51eGR6dHl5Z2UuanBn.jpg" alt="Rock and Roll Hall of Fame Music Masters 2015: Date, Time and How to Watch Online"></div><figcaption class="article-embeddable-caption">Smokey Robinson</figcaption><figcaption class="article-embeddable-attribution">Source:&nbsp;<a href="http://www.gettyimages.com/" class="article-embeddable-source">Paras Griffin/Getty Images</a></figcaption></figure></div>
